  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human male of bronze skin, compactly built and broad through the shoulders from years of barrel-work and counter service. Brown eyes sit beneath heavy brows, giving the face a settled, appraising cast reinforced by a square jaw and a straight, slightly flattened nose. Brown hair is kept in a short, practical cut, receding lightly at the temples and worn in a plain style that emphasizes function over display. The hands are notably thick-fingered and callused, with small, old nicks along the knuckles consistent with routine work among glass, cask iron, and rough-sawn timber.",
